description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Frog on hydrangea
-White-eye and plum blossoms
-Yellow swallowtail butterfly and cosmos
-Ladybug on a daisy flower
-Mantis on a rose
-Dragonfly and begonia grandis
-Honeybee and sunflower
-Sparrow and cherry blossoms
-Snail on hydrangea
-Chinese peacock butterfly and abelia
name: Flowers & Organisms
